  <description><![CDATA[<p>A superb slope-side complex offering classic, yet modern deluxe studios, one and two bedroom condos.</p>
<p>Resort offers many shops and choice of restaurants to eat breakfast, lunch and dinner.</p>
<p>Beaver Run Resort has unique indoor/outdoor pool, seven mountain view hot tubs, spa with sauna, steam room and fitness room.</p>
<p>From the base of Peak Nine you can take teh High speed Quad chairlift.</p>]]></description>
