  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>
<h4>Types of accommodation:</h4>
</li>
<li><strong>Deluxe Studio - sleeps 1-4 </strong>One queen bed in sleeping area visually separated (no door) from living area with queen sofa bed. Bathroom with whirlpool bath and wc and mini kitchenette.</li>
<li><strong>1-bedroom Condo - sleeps 2-4</strong> Bedroom with queen bed, living area with queen sofa bed, bathroom with bath and wc and complete kitchen.</li>
<li><strong>2-bedroom Condo - sleeps 3-6 </strong>One bedroom with queen bed and en suite bathroom, bedroom with two queen beds and living room with queen sofa bed. Second bathroom with bath and wc and complete kitchen.</li>
<li><strong>Included: </strong>Linen, towels and daily cleaning.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
